        <p class="lead">Brunaþéttingar is a specialised technical insulation and fire sealing company serving contractors, building owners and operators across Iceland. <strong>We do not offer fire engineering</strong> — that work belongs to fire engineers. We advise on materials and solutions, and we execute the work. For fire engineering we specifically recommend <strong>Tensio Architects</strong>.</p>
