<section class="process">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="head">
      <div class="label">End-to-end service</div>
      <h2>From the first drawing to final inspection — one team, one process.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="num">01</div>
        <h4>Fire engineering &amp; advice</h4>
        <p>We do not offer fire engineering design — that is done by fire engineers. We advise on solutions and material selection. We specifically recommend <strong>Tensio Architects</strong> for fire engineering.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="num">02</div>
        <h4>Planning</h4>
        <p>Brunaþéttingar plan the job — material selection, quantities, timelines and coordination with other contractors, based on drawings and site conditions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="num">03</div>
        <h4>Project management &amp; installation</h4>
        <p>Our project manager runs the work on site. Certified fire-sealing installers work with ETA-certified systems from leading manufacturers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="num">04</div>
        <h4>Documentation &amp; reporting</h4>
        <p>Every seal is tracked in our documentation system with photo, GPS, certification number and date. The final report is delivered to the owner and to the fire authority for inspection.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

