        <h2>Documentation is the <span class="ul">heart of the service</span>.</h2>
        <p>Documentation and reporting are what set Brunaþéttingar apart. We produce two distinct types of reports for our clients:</p>
        <p><strong>Inspection reports</strong> — independent assessments of the condition of fire sealing in existing buildings. Suited to owners who need a complete overview ahead of a fire authority inspection or maintenance planning.</p>
        <p><strong>Project handover reports</strong> — delivered with every single project. They include photos of each seal, location on the drawing, certification numbers of the systems used, and the installation date.</p>
